title: Emmanuel Macron Extends French Coronavirus Lockdown Until May 11
description: French President Emmanuel Macron has announced that the emergency measures to stem the spread of the Wuhan virus will be kept in place for an additional month while admitting that the government was not prepared for the pandemic.
